strings: <voice_0x01001707><se_low>January: Stand up and come. The princess looks a bit confused.
<voice_0x01001708><se_low>January: We've come a long way, you should at least try to "see" everything.
<voice_0x01001709><se_low>January: Come here, I'll be waiting for you at the church.
<voice_0x0100170A><se_def>China: I thought he would not come, but it was already dark.
<voice_0x0100170B><se_def>China: i am with you. No one will see you in a crowd.
<voice_0x0100170C><se_def>*: How much is it? I can't see anything here!
<voice_0x0100170D><se_def>*: Finally something happened! start with it
<voice_0x0100170E><se_high>*: The people praised the bride for being so beautiful! I wish I could have liked him a little more!
<voice_0x0100170F><se_low>*: I was more interested in the appearance of the new high priest than the bride and groom. I can see nothing here!
<voice_0x01001710><se_def>*: Happy birthday Princess Mediah! happy birthday prince charming
<voice_0x01001711><se_high>*: Oh, calm down!
<voice_0x01001713><se_low>January: Hello my god! Should they get there!
<voice_0x01001714><se_low>January: O Follow me
<voice_0x01001715><se_low>January: hi...
<voice_0x01001716><se_low>January: We've gone too far, we have to defend ourselves tonight...
<voice_0x0100189D><se_def>China: Hi, I wonder if you'll leave us forever. When you came back yesterday, it looked like you were ready to give up. But better, I understand!
<voice_0x0100189E><se_def>China: It seemed that the festival had already started.
<voice_0x0100189F><se_def>China: And I suspect many people can do it if they want.
<voice_0x010018A0><se_def>China: You never dated Jessica, did you?
<voice_0x010018A1><se_def>China: The princess called me yesterday and since then I haven't seen her.
<voice_0x010018A2><se_def>China: The payment terms are expected to be the same. You probably haven't met him yet, have you?
